<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.8.5">
<l>taḷirniṟattāṟ kuṟaivillāt taṉicciṟaiyil viḷappuṟṟa</l>
<l>kiḷimoḻiyāṭ kāraṇamāk kiḷararakka ṉakareritta</l>
<l>kaḷimalart tuḻāyalaṅkaṟ kamaḻmuṭiyaṉ kaṭalñālat</l>
<l>taḷimikkāṉ kavarāta vaṟiviṉāṟ kuṟaivilamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except of the want for [our] sprout colour</l>
<l>we have no want for [our] knowledge that is not seized by the one exceeding in care</l>
<l>for the ocean[-girdled], he with a fragrant crown wreathed with Tulsi in nectar blossoms</l> 
<l>who burned the city of the exalted Rakṣasa, because of her with parrot words</l>
	<l>who was famous in [her] solitary prison.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
